intent.user_query: What product types have the most open service tickets? This highlights potential quality issues for specific product categories, which might impact marketing messages.

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductType, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS OpenTicketCount FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.Status = 'Open' GROUP BY p.ProductType ORDER BY OpenTicketCount DESC;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductType, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS OpenTicketCount FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.Status = 'Open' GROUP BY p.ProductType ORDER BY OpenTicketCount DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
